---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle} title={pageTitle}>
  <ImageContainer url={headshot} alt="jj headshot" width="180" />
  <p class="mb-8 text-xl">üíª Web Developer. ‚ù§Ô∏è Coach. üê∂ Dog Dad.</p>
